<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965125>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Adults of Siberian Geometrinae. A—Hemithea aestivaria; B—Dyschloropsis impararia; C—Chlorissa viridata; D—C. obliterata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965184>
    dc:description "FIGURE 35. Male genitalia of Siberian Geometrinae. A—Thalera chlorosaria; B, C—Dyschloropsis impararia; D, E, H, I—Chlorissa viridata; F, G, J—C. obliterata. A, B, D, F—genital segment; C, E, G—phallos; H–J—sternite A8. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965184/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965186>
    dc:description "FIGURE 36. Male genitalia of Siberian Geometrinae. A–D, I, J—Chlorissa viridata; E–H, K, L—C. obliterata. A, B, E, F—vinculum, lateral view; C, D, G, H—phallos; I–L—left valva. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965186/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965190>
    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Female genitalia of Siberian Geometrinae. A—Jodis lactearia; B—J. putata; C—Thalera fimbrialis; D—T. chlorosaria; E—Dyschloropsis impararia; F—Chlorissa viridata; G—C. obliterata. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965190/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

